# Memorix Application Guidelines

## Project Documentation
For full documentation on the Memorix project, please refer to the files in the .cursor/rules directory or the docs folder.

## Styling Guidelines
- Use Tailwind CSS exclusively for styling
- Follow the color scheme with primary accent color #00ff94
- Use responsive design with Tailwind modifiers
- Ensure components are accessible

## Component Creation
- Create functional components with React hooks
- Follow the established project structure
- Organize imports: React first, third-party libraries second, local components last

## Documentation
- All new features should be well documented
- Reference the style-guide.md for design guidelines
- Use JSDoc comments for complex functions 